- Kau lupa? Kau?

12
00:00:23,791 --> 00:00:25,124
Apa kau bercanda?!

13
00:00:25,126 --> 00:00:26,125
Katakan di mana kau.

14
00:00:26,127 --> 00:00:28,294
Aku dekat, Sherlock.

15
00:00:34,035 --> 00:00:36,068
Maaf tentang semalam.

16
00:00:36,070 --> 00:00:37,970
Kau tidak berbuat apa-apa.
Itu salahku.

17
00:00:37,972 --> 00:00:39,705
Kau tidak sehat.

18
